ana\n|-\n| colspan=2| ''Tee Shirt Man'' || data-sort-value=\"Rasoanaivo\"| Tovoniaina Rasoanaivo || Madagascar\n|}\n\n===Special Screenings===\nThe following films were the Special Screenings of the Official Selection:<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/special-screenings |title=Special Screenings |work=labiennale.org |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140927233711/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/special-screenings |archivedate=27 September 2014 |access-date=13 April 2018  }}</ref>\n* ''9x10 novanta'', by various Italian directors. A film composed of footages from the Luce Archives, to celebrate the 90th anniversary of the Luce Institute. It was presented in collaboration with Venice Days (see also section below).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.venice-days.com/2014/film.asp?id=12&id_dettaglio=419&t=9x10%20NOVANTA&lang=eng |title=Special Events, 9x10 NOVANTA |work=venice-days.com |accessdate=13 April 2018}}</ref>\n* ''Taipei Factory II'' by Hou Chi-Jan, Cho Li, and Hsieh Chun-Yi (Chinese Taipei)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/special-screenings/taipei-factory-ii.html |title=Taipei Factory II - Alla scoperta di Taipei by Hou Chi-jan, Cho Li, Hsieh Chun-yi |work=labiennale.org |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828221628/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/special-screenings/taipei-factory-ii.html |archivedate=28 August 2014 |access-date=13 April 2018  }}</ref>\n\n==Autonomous sections==\n===International Critics\u2019 Week===\nThe following films were selected for the 29th Venice International Film Critics' Week:<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sicvenezia.it/edizione/29-settimana-internazionale-della-critica/?lang=en |title=29th International Film Critics\u2019 Week |work=sicvenezia.it |accessdate=11 April 2018}}</ref><ref name=\"Criticsweek\">{{cite web